	STANDARD SUPPORT MODULES
==============================================================================

MODULE:  EPICS base
VERSION: 3-14-7
BUILD DEPENDENCIES: Tornado 2.0.2

MODULE:  vxStats
VERSION: 1-7-2c
SOURCE:  modification of ics-web1.sns.ornl.gov/share/vxStats314.tar.gz
BUILD DEPENDENCIES: EPICS_BASE
PROCEDURE:
	cd <supporttop>/vxStats;
	tar xf <supporttop>/TAR/vxStatsR1-7-2c.tar

	(See vxStats/releaseNotes.txt for changes from the
	original distribution, vxStats314.tar)

MODULE:  seq
VERSION: 2-0-10
SOURCE:  www.slac.stanford.edu/comp/unix/package/epics/sequencer/
BUILD DEPENDENCIES: EPICS_BASE
PROCEDURE:
- After unzipping and untarring seq-2.0.10.tar.gz;
	cd <supporttop>;
	mv seq-2.0.10 seq/2-0-10

